# Kunitz Domain Identification and Analysis

This repository contains code and data to identify and analyze **Kunitz-type protease inhibitor domains** using profile Hidden Markov Models (HMMs). The project is part of the Laboratory of Bioinformatics I course at the University of Bologna, within the master's degree in Bioinformatics.

